Game of 2 player Tic-Tac-Toe

1. Game should be written to support expanding the game board from 3x3 to something larger like 10x10.
2. Win criteria should be configurable too so that it can increase from 3 in a row to 10 in a row.
3. Game state should be save-able and load-able. 
4. Player should be able to reload a saved game and start playing from the saved state.